---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Projects | Dan Ryan Neff"
  description="Projects exploring creativity, digital identity, and possibilities for the web."
>
  <main>
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="px-6 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p
            class="mb-5 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            Projects
          </p>

          <h1
            class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl"
          >
            Exploring ideas by building them.
          </h1>

          <p
            class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            These projects explore different aspects of the same question:
          </p>

          <blockquote
            class="mt-8 border-l-2 border-gray-300 pl-6 text-2xl leading-relaxed text-gray-900 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-100"
          >
            What does it mean to participate well in a technological world?
          </blockquote>

          <p
            class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            Some are software. Some are experiments. Some are ongoing
            practices. Each has taught me something about how people interact
            with technology—and with one another.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mandalafy -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div
        class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] lg:gap-20"
      >
        <div>
          <p
            class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            Creative practice
          </p>

          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
          >
            Mandalafy
          </h2>

          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            Mandalafy began as an exploration of generative art and has become
            an ongoing creative practice. Through patterns, symmetry, and
            color, it explores attention, beauty, and the pleasure of making.
          </p>

          <p
            class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            It reminds me that technology can be more than a tool for
            productivity. It can also be a medium for creativity, reflection,
            and wonder.
          </p>
        </div>

        <figure>
          <img
            src="/images/mandala-woven-sunlight-660.webp"
            alt="A colorful geometric mandala created through the Mandalafy project"
            class="mx-auto w-full max-w-md rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LandingBio -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div
        class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1fr] lg:gap-20"
      >
        <figure class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/images/dot-compilation.webp"
            alt="An abstract composition of colorful dots and connected forms"
            class="mx-auto w-full max-w-md rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p
            class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            Digital identity
          </p>

          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
          >
            LandingBio
          </h2>

          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            LandingBio helps people create a simple home for themselves on the
            web. Instead of chasing algorithms or optimizing for attention, it
            encourages clarity, authenticity, and ownership.
          </p>

          <p
            class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            It is an exploration of digital identity and what it means to have
            a place online that genuinely reflects who you are.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ImagineThis.Site -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
      <div
        class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_0.9fr] lg:gap-20"
      >
        <div>
          <p
            class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            Exploring possibilities
          </p>

          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
          >
            ImagineThis.Site
          </h2>

          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            ImagineThis.Site is where I build concept websites that explore
            what the web could become. It’s a space for experimenting with
            ideas and, over time, helping others imagine websites of their own.
          </p>
        </div>

        <figure>
          <img
            src="/images/VividRhythms.webp"
            alt="An expressive abstract artwork with layered shapes and vivid visual rhythms"
            class="mx-auto w-full max-w-md rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Connections -->
    <section class="px-6 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div
        class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:gap-20"
      >
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/images/SubtleCircles.webp"
            alt="A subtle arrangement of overlapping circular forms"
            class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm opacity-90"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>

        <div>
          <p
            class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            A shared curiosity
          </p>

          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
          >
            What connects these projects?
          </h2>

          <p
            class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            Although they look different, they all grow from a related set of
            questions.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 space-y-5">
            <p
              class="border-l-2 border-gray-300 pl-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
            >
              How can technology help people participate more fully?
            </p>

            <p
              class="border-l-2 border-gray-300 pl-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
            >
              How do digital tools shape human relationships?
            </p>

            <p
              class="border-l-2 border-gray-300 pl-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
            >
              How can we design technology that invites curiosity rather than
              distraction?
            </p>

            <p
              class="border-l-2 border-gray-300 pl-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
            >
              What makes a digital place feel welcoming?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What's Next -->
    <section class="px-6 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <p
            class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            Ongoing
          </p>

          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl"
          >
            What’s next?
          </h2>

          <p
            class="mt-6 text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
          >
            I’m always exploring new ideas at the intersection of people and
            technology. Some become projects. Others become conversations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>